    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your presence has been noticed. Your descent begins. What current compels you to help our detective, Madeleine, solve a buried case? Be weary, beneath the streets of Paris lies a realm that will help and hinder you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/97dc9c8a3fdfe485733747d0220b7919.poster.avif?t=1763474316\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/97dc9c8a3fdfe485733747d0220b7919.webm?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/97dc9c8a3fdfe485733747d0220b7919.mp4?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced Freefall Combat</strong>: Dash, grapple, and slide as you plummet deeper into the unknown, fighting to stay alive against relentless enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/7be929bfcfc137a65b1fe10285161a81.poster.avif?t=1763474316\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/7be929bfcfc137a65b1fe10285161a81.webm?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/7be929bfcfc137a65b1fe10285161a81.mp4?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Curse-laden Blessings</strong>: Find mysterious boons that grant new powers. Be wary of what you decide to take however, some blessings are double-edged, and have consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/32015632a154941630d25a8244c3d3c7.poster.avif?t=1763474316\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/32015632a154941630d25a8244c3d3c7.webm?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/32015632a154941630d25a8244c3d3c7.mp4?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Surreal Exploration</strong>: Discover a surreal, nightmarish labyrinth beneath the streets of Paris; a twisting underworld teeming with secrets to uncover, and where something is always watching.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/e45bf10bf6c39b7e971ebacb9c8df857.poster.avif?t=1763474316\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/e45bf10bf6c39b7e971ebacb9c8df857.webm?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/e45bf10bf6c39b7e971ebacb9c8df857.mp4?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Life as Currency</strong>: Your life is a resource. Spend it wisely to gain power, but risk losing everything if you go too far.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/01204ff112c3344485810a417d74c072.poster.avif?t=1763474316\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/01204ff112c3344485810a417d74c072.webm?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288890/extras/01204ff112c3344485810a417d74c072.mp4?t=1763474316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Noir meets Eldritch Horror</strong>: A unique blend of noir mystery, gothic atmosphere, and  eldritch horror. Can you survive the descent and unravel the secrets of the underground tunnels; or will you lose yourself and be forgotten forever?</p>",
